    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut your <strong>pork belly</strong> lengthways into 3 slices per person and then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Season with<strong> </strong>a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sriracha-and-honey-pork-belly-with-smoked-salt-sweet-potato-chips-and-slaw/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pork belly slices </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>and cover with <strong>tin foil</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for an initial 20-25 min</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sriracha-and-honey-pork-belly-with-smoked-salt-sweet-potato-chips-and-slaw/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into chips</p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sriracha-and-honey-pork-belly-with-smoked-salt-sweet-potato-chips-and-slaw/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile combine your <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>honey </strong>in a small bowl with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>sriracha honey glaze</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sriracha-and-honey-pork-belly-with-smoked-salt-sweet-potato-chips-and-slaw/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>apple[s]</strong> (skin on) into matchsticks</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sriracha-and-honey-pork-belly-with-smoked-salt-sweet-potato-chips-and-slaw/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped apple</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>mayo </strong>and<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>white wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your<strong> slaw</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sriracha-and-honey-pork-belly-with-smoked-salt-sweet-potato-chips-and-slaw/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the pork has had an initial 20 min remove the dish from the oven and remove the tin foil</p><p>Add the <strong>sriracha honey glaze</strong> and give everything a mix up until fully coated</p><p>Return the dish to the oven, uncovered, for a further 10-12 min or until browned and cooked through (no pink meat!) \u2013 this is your <strong>sticky sriracha & honey pork belly</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sriracha-and-honey-pork-belly-with-smoked-salt-sweet-potato-chips-and-slaw/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Sprinkle your <strong>smoked sea salt flakes </strong>over the <strong>chips </strong>\u2013 these are your <strong>smoked salt chips</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>sticky sriracha & honey pork belly </strong>with the <strong>slaw</strong> and <strong>smoked salt chips </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
